        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        📄 Hey There Delilah – Gitarrennoten
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1lNqy2Y4COd17pg6RmeuMM6_ej3Nxlu74"
        class="cta-button"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
